# Optional overrides (defaults point at darrenadixonpi/AI-stack-map)
# VITE_GITHUB_REPO=darrenadixonpi/AI-stack-map

# ── Suggest-an-edit auto-submit (api/suggest.ts, Vercel) ──
# Server-side ONLY — never prefix these with VITE_ (that would expose them to the browser).
# Fine-grained PAT (or GitHub App token) with "Issues: write" on the repo:
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_xxx
# Repo to file issues in (optional; defaults to darrenadixonpi/AI-stack-map):
# GITHUB_REPO=darrenadixonpi/AI-stack-map
# Issue label (optional; defaults to "content"):
# SUGGEST_LABEL=content
